---

<RoomLayout
  title="Le Petit Mas: Family Suite | Mas du Chanoine"
  description="Family suite for 3 guests: two bedrooms in an independent building in the Mediterranean garden facing the basin"
  lang="en"
  alternates={{ fr: '/chambres-hotes/petit-mas/', en: '/en/chambres-hotes/petit-mas-family-suite/', it: '/it/chambres-hotes/petit-mas-familiare-suite/' }}
  roomName="LE PETIT MAS"
  subtitle="Independent & Family-friendly"
  tagline="Independent building with 2 bedrooms, for people traveling in threes, overlooking the basin"
  heroImage="/media/chambres/chambre-petit-mas.jpg"
  amenities={amenities}
  amenitiesTitle="Room Equipment"
  amenitiesSummary="Surface: 35 m² — 2 bedrooms — Ground floor"
  gallery={gallery}
  galleryTitle="Photo Gallery"
  bookingLabel="Book this room"
  otherRoomsTitle="Discover our other rooms"
  otherRoomsLabel="View all rooms"
  otherRoomsUrl="/en/bed-breakfast/"
  breadcrumb={[
    { label: 'Home', href: '/en/' },
    { label: 'Rooms', href: '/en/bed-breakfast/' },
    { label: 'Le Petit Mas' },
  ]}
>
  <p>Located in an independent building, next to the fish basin, Le Petit Mas is an ideal family suite to accommodate people traveling in threes: 3 adults, or two adults with a child over 12 years old. The two separate bedrooms guarantee everyone's privacy.</p>
  <p>Over 35 m², you have: a bedroom with a King Size bed (180×200), air conditioning, flat screen TV, Wi-Fi, tea and coffee facilities, mini-fridge, safe, and a desk; a bedroom with a Queen Size bed (160×200) and an armchair; a walk-in shower room; a separate toilet.</p>
  <p>Both bedrooms have shelves and large sliding wardrobes for your comfort. In front of Le Petit Mas, you can enjoy garden furniture.</p>
</RoomLayout>
